PUT {{baseUrl}}/update
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "score": 4,
  "content": "修改后的评价内容",
  "images": [
    "/static/uploadImages/comment/3.jpg"
  ],
  "isAnonymous": "N"
}

### 5. 删除评价
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/delete
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "userId": 1
}

### 6. 商家回复评价
POST {{baseUrl}}/reply
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "replyContent": "感谢您的支持，期待您再次光临！",
