### 7. 获取商品评价统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 8. 查询用户评价列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 9. 查询商品评价列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/goods/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 10. 检查是否已评价
GET {{baseUrl}}/check?orderId=1&goodsId=1&userId=1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 11. 点赞评价
POST {{baseUrl}}/like/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 12. 获取店铺NPS统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/nps/store/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 13. 获取商户NPS统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/nps/merchant/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 14. 获取商户价格统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/price/merchant/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
